1. Not too slow, not too fast training 2. PVP (No drops but I made safe zones in varrock with some of the buildings. You will need to make a tele there though) 3. Pretty stable, doesn't allow usernames with symbols such as & or @ or / etc... 4. Shops aren't too great, so stable economy 5. Training area is at the blue portal, cows for beginners and giant skeles for higher levels 6. The emote tabs aren't filled with like "PK" and stuff, it's just drags, drags2, and home. (I believe that is all) 7. Lumbridge as starting area 8. D claws spec 9. Lots of tools, lists, and even bat. files that make minigames for you! 10. Custom added slayer 11. Castle wars as funPK area 12. MUCH MUCH MORE!!
[b]IT IS NOT A DELTA SOURCE, THE SENDMESSAGES ARE "SM" BUT IT IS NOT A DELTA SOURCE! I JUST REPLACED IT![/b]

Anyways, you will have to add d claws and stuff, i might release client later.
